-family:var(--font-callingbox-mono)">CallingBox</span></div><p class="mt-5 text-[30px] font-semibold leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.04em] text-[#f4f4f5] sm:text-[36px]">The API for AI phone calls</p><p class="mt-4 max-w-[420px] text-[15px] leading-[1.7] text-[#a1a1aa]">Give your AI agents a phone number and let them make calls for you.</p><div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3"><a href="https://callingbox.io/?utm_source=llm-stats&amp;utm_medium=promo_card&amp;utm_campaign=homepage&amp;utm_content=lg" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="rounded-full bg-[#f4f4f5] px-7 py-2.5 text-[14px] font-medium text-[#18181b] transition-colors hover:bg-[#d4d4d8] focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-[#a1a1aa]">Start for free</a><a href="https://docs.callingbox.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="rounded-full border border-[#3f3f46] px-7 py-2.5 text-[14px] font-medium text-[#a1a1aa] transition-colors hover:border-[#52525b] hover:text-[#f4f4f5] focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-[#a1a1aa]">Read the docs</a></div><div class="mt-7 flex items-center gap-5 text-[13px] text-[#52525b]"><span><span class="font-medium text-[#a1a1aa]">$0.05</span> /min all-in</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="h-3.5 w-px bg-[#27272a]"></span><span><span class="font-medium text-[#a1a1aa]">7 lines</span> of code</span></div></div><div class="min-w-0"><style>
@keyframes cb-scan {
  0%   { transform: translateY(-12%); opacity: 0; }
  12%  { opacity: 1; }
  88%  { opacity: 1; }
  100% { transform: translateY(112%); opacity: 0; }
}
@keyframes cb-breath {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.35; }
  50%      { opacity: 1; }
}
@keyframes cb-ping {
  0%   { transform: scale(1);   opacity: 0.55; }
  100% { transform: scale(2.6); opacity: 0; }
}
@keyframes cb-draw {
  from { stroke-dashoffset: 1; }
  to   { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
}
@keyframes cb-rise {
  from { transform: translateY(6px); opacity: 0; }
  to   { transform: translateY(0);   opacity: 1; }
}
@keyframes cb-fade-in {
  from { opacity: 0; }
  to   { opacity: 1; }
}
@keyframes cb-orbit-x {
  0%   { left: 0%;                opacity: 0; }
  15%  { opacity: 1; }
  85%  { opacity: 1; }
  100% { left: calc(100% - 6px);  opacity: 0; }
}
.cb-scan      { animation: cb-scan 1.0s cubic-bezier(0.32, 0, 0.32, 1) both; }
.cb-breath    { animation: cb-breath 2.4s ease-in-out infinite; }
.cb-ping      { animation: cb-ping 1.8s cubic-bezier(0.32, 0, 0.32, 1) infinite; }
.cb-draw      { stroke-dasharray: 1; animation: cb-draw 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.32, 0, 0.32, 1) both; }
.cb-rise      { animation: cb-rise 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) both; }
.cb-fade-in   { animation: cb-fade-in 0.45s ease both; }
.cb-orbit     { animation: cb-orbit-x 1.4s linear infinite; }
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .cb-scan, .cb-breath, .cb-ping, .cb-draw, .cb-rise, .cb-fade-in, .cb-orbit {
    animation: none !important;
  }
}
</style><div class="rounded-2xl bg-[#1f1f23] ring-1 ring-[#27272a]"><div class="flex items-center px-4 pt-2.5 pb-0"><div class="mr-5 flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="h-[9px] w-[9px] rounded-full bg-white/[0.06]"></span><span class="h-[9px] w-[9px] rounded-full bg-white/[0.06]"></span><span class="h-[9px] w-[9px] rounded-full bg-white/[0.06]"></span></div><div class="flex"><button type="button" class="relative px-3.5 py-1.5 text-[12px] font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-[#a1a1aa] text-[#a1a1aa]">Python<span class="absolute bottom-0 left-3 right-3 h-px bg-[#3f3f46]"></span></button><button type="button" class="relative px-3.5 py-1.5 text-[12px] font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-[#a1a1aa] text-[#3f3f46] hover:text-[#71717a]">TypeScript</button><button type="button" class="relative px-3.5 py-1.5 text-[12px] font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-[#a1a1aa] text-[#3f3f46] hover:text-[#71717a]">cURL</button><button type="button" class="relative px-3.5 py-1.5 text-[12px] font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-[#a1a1aa] text-[#3f3f46] hover:text-[#71717a]">CLI</button></div></div><div class="mx-1 mt-1 mb-1 rounded-b-2xl bg-[#1c1c20]"><div class="relative overflow-hidden px-6 py-5 text-[13px] leading-[2.1] whitespace-pre" style="font-family:var(--font-callingbox-mono)"><div class="text-[#71717a]"><span class="text-[#c4b5fd]">from</span> <span class="text-[#d4d4d8]">callingbox</span> <span class="text-[#c4b5fd]">import</span> <span class="text-[#d4d4d8]">Callingbox</span></div><div class="h-3"></div><div class="text-[#71717a]"><span class="text-[#d4d4d8]">client</span> <span class="text-[#52525b]">=</span> <